metadata.name: TRAVEL #1
metadata.description:
It was a very peaceful place. The chirping of the birds and the sound of the flowing water of the small waterfall made all the hustle and bustle of my worries go away.
Usually, when I go on a trip, my head is filled with questions about the next destination, but here I felt like I could forget everything and look at the mountains for a few days without a purpose.

* Two AI system works together to create this wide ink landscape.
